---
title: Turkey Tacos with Salsa and Salad
description: Pork carnitas is a traditional Mexican dish of slow-cooked pork shoulder that's shredded and pan-fried to give it a crispy texture. We've created a quick, kid-friendly version using ground turkey. The secret is cooking the meat until it's dark brown!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-tacos-9a9a4d58.jpg
